CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16, reads: "D.I.'s 'Atlantic City, USA' Thrills Patrons at Press Club Summer Revue"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gloria Golden Grate wearing light colored dress with three quarter length sleeves, gloves, and hat, standing in interior of her home in preparation of the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A," held in the Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn
